'''朱蓮'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Kalanchoe sexangularis}}''）為[[景天科|景天科]][[伽蓝菜属|伽蓝菜属]]的物種。為[[多年生|多年生]][[常綠|常綠]][[亞灌木|亞灌木]][[肉質植物|肉質植物]]，原產於[[非洲|非洲]]東南部。<ref>[http://eol.org/data_objects/21283590 Point Map of Kalanchoe sexangularis] {{Wayback|url=http://eol.org/data_objects/21283590 |date=20160306023129 }}http://eol.org {{Wayback|url=http://eol.org/ |date=20110722170736 }} 朱蓮野生分佈地點</ref>

==形態==
植株可高達0.6米至1米，根幼細而根系發達<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.plantegrassefrontignan.fr/plantes%20grasses%20mediterranennes/fiches/Kalanchoe%20sexangularis.html |title=Mediterranean succulents - Kalanchoe and Kalankoe |access-date=2014-03-15 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202184130/http://www.plantegrassefrontignan.fr/plantes%20grasses%20mediterranennes/fiches/Kalanchoe%20sexangularis.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，葉無毛，葉為橢圓形，綠色，葉邊緣為紅色，當溫差大及日照充足時全葉變為紅色，葉片邊緣為鈍齒狀，花黃色<ref>[http://eol.org/data_objects/13263463 朱蓮開花圖片] {{Wayback|url=http://eol.org/data_objects/13263463 |date=20140315071243 }}http://eol.org/ {{Wayback|url=http://eol.org/ |date=20110722170736 }}</ref>，花期為[[冬季|冬季]]至[[春季|春季]]。<ref name="Kalanchoe sexangularis">[http://plants.jstor.org/taxon/kalanchoe.sexangularis Kalanchoe sexangularis]Global Plants (formerly JSTOR Plant Science)</ref><ref>[http://www.smgrowers.com/products/plants/plantdisplay.asp?plant_id=3580 Kalanchoe sexangularis - Six-angled Kalanchoe] {{Wayback|url=http://www.smgrowers.com/products/plants/plantdisplay.asp?plant_id=3580 |date=20170303134855 }}San Marcos Growers</ref>

==特性==
朱蓮為肉質植物，十分耐旱及耐寒，可抵禦[[華氏|華氏]]20至25度(大約[[攝氏|攝氏]]-4至-6度)的低溫。<ref>[http://kumbulanursery.co.za/plants/kalanchoe-sexangularis Kalanchoe sexangularis] {{Wayback|url=http://kumbulanursery.co.za/plants/kalanchoe-sexangularis |date=20201023104855 }}Kumbula Indigenous Nursery</ref>

==分佈==
野生分佈於[[南非|南非]][[納塔爾省|納塔爾省]]東部及[[津巴布韋|津巴布韋]]，生長於山頂或山脊岩石坡的灌木叢中。<ref name="Kalanchoe sexangularis"/>

